<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n09049e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n09" href="#n09049e">N09 (VI.B.1)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n09all.htm#n09049e"> 49(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Grande Chartreuse 1 a year / the long walk all day</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><b>Monk&apos;s Health Secrets</b>. &hellip; Smoking is utterly eschewed, and the only spirit taken is a little <mark>Grande Chartreuse on New Year&apos;s Day</mark> and after the <mark>&ldquo;long walk,&rdquo; which occurs once a year and lasts all day</mark>. <small> <a name="FJ25feb24" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#FJ25feb24"><cite title="source">Freeman's Journal</cite></a> (25 February 1924) 7/6</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
